phodav (WebDav server implementation using libsoup - RFC 4918)

Phodav is a WebDav server implementation using libsoup (RFC 4918).
It provides chezdav, a tool that allows to share a particular
directory (with optional digest authentication).

HOME: https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/phodav

